headline: Eastman Chemical (EMN) Q4 Earnings and Revenues Miss Estimates
summary: Eastman Chemical (EMN) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of -1.68% and -3.15%, respectively, for the quarter ended December 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
